{"tid":1550753,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵人傾吓計啊！！","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:27:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T18:28:27.000Z","uid":217764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1306f91ae1150a7ed95deefcdc13053057a3bdda","tid":1550753,"uid":217764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:27:18.000Z","msg":"生活愈嚟愈悶<br />\n近排我地嘅香港又發生好多事 每一日個情緒都好down<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家開sem啦 發現可以傾計嘅人好少 <br />\n想同人share每日近況同心情都冇 個人好冇動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申第一次開post sorry for 1999"},{"pid":"fca4f6ab3f4d4d55c0a30c0a674aaa05774060c9","tid":1550753,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:28:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19a03a9430662509449142c76930a5843c403cea","tid":1550753,"uid":241106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:33:57.000Z","msg":"黎啦"},{"pid":"69d753d16faa7d3bc16f6755780fc526ee08774b","tid":1550753,"uid":124811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:35:09.000Z","msg":"你肯講 我肯聽"},{"pid":"109c87a